		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In the debugger, have it break on the song init address from the NSF(0x08 in NSF)
<br />
<br />Load the NSF, set the breakpoint, then reset emulation.
<br />
<br />When it hits the song init breakpoint, add a breakpoint for 381E
<br />
<br />Go into the trace logger, start it, then press Run in the debugger.
<br />
<br />The fault should be easier to find, or obvious.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
